Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,January 21, 2017, became a special day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for deaf people in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah’s Witnesses released\Nthe book of Matthew
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in Japanese Sign Language.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What, though, was behind these smiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When I used to read the Japanese Bible,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I really didn’t understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so I forced myself to read—not much of a joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it was hard to understand\Nand explain to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bible, written in a language\Nwe do not know, will not move our heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Having no sign-language Bible
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was a huge disadvantage\Nwhen it came to cultivating a longing for God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When making shepherding calls,\Nreasoning on a scripture
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with a deaf person was difficult if that scripture
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn’t translated into sign language.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a Bible in American Sign Language,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was envious and wanted to see the Bible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in Japanese Sign Language so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, approval was given for Bible translation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,into Japanese Sign Language.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that the translation team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,offered a prayer\Nbefore they started each day’s work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, when faced\Nwith difficult translation problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they relied on Jehovah’s holy spirit\Nthrough prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they could exercise good judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are various processes\Nneeded for God’s Word
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to jump off the page\Nand reach the heart of deaf people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They considered carefully\N how to express scriptures
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so that deaf people would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s take an example:\N“the lilies of the field” at Matthew 6:28.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn’t able to understand\NMatthew chapter 6 until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought,\N‘“Birds of heaven” and “lilies of the field,”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they have to do\Nwith “seeking first the Kingdom”?’
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The translators individually read and research
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the source text\Nto fully understand what they’ll translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the team meets to discuss the text
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and explore ideas\Nfor translating certain concepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After the translation is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the assigned brother signs the translation\Nto prepare the prompt video.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then studio recording takes place,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,referencing the prompt video.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The recorded movie is carefully edited
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and prepared for delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the signer pretends to be a flower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and weaves his own petals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and sews them on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he asks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“Flowers don’t do that, do they?”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God’s Word coming off the pages
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,has reached the heart of deaf people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood for the first time\Nthat Jehovah is kindly teaching us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‘If you seek the Kingdom first,\NI’ll give you everything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.’
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching it\Non the train on my way to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, ‘Wow, this is so good!’
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was absorbed in the video,\Nand I missed my train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I changed trains, but again,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching the video\Nand missed my station again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The book of Matthew is that interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans have beneficial feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because we are created in God’s image.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:04:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of Satan’s system of things,\Nthese feelings are driven away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when you show God’s Word\Nto people or read it yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,innate beneficial feelings\Nwell up in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I strongly feel that God’s Word\Nhas the power to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a child grows up\Nlistening to what their father says,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be closer to my Father,\NJehovah, by watching him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,speak to me\Nin my native tongue, sign language.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Comments from deaf brothers show
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that the sign-language Bible\Ntalks to their heart directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine that Jehovah loves our brothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and his face is shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the faces of our brothers\Nare also shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now by means of having God’s living Word
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in the language of their heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,our deaf brothers and sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,are seeing Jehovah’s face shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:06.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,2017年1月21日は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.32,0:00:09.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,日本のろう者にとって\N特別な日となりました
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:13.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバの証人が日本手話版の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:16.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,「マタイによる福音書」を\N発表したのです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:21.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,これほどの笑顔があふれたのは\Nなぜでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,日本語の聖書は意味が\Nよく分かりませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,仕方なく読んではいましたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:31.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,楽しくはなかったです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:35.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,意味をつかんで人に説明\Nするのが難しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,分からない言語で聖書を読んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:41.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,それは心を動かしません
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,神のことを慕う気持ちを\N培うという点では
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:49.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,手話という言語での聖書がないって\Nいうことはとても不利だったと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,牧羊訪問でも この聖句を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:55.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,ろう者の方と推論して\N考えたいと思っても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:59.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,その聖句がないので 難しさは\N大きかったと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:05.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,アメリカ手話版は出ていたので\Nうらやましく感じていました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:10.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,ぜひ日本手話でも聖書を見たいと\N待ち望んでいました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:17.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,ついに 聖書の日本手話版の\N翻訳が承認されました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,翻訳チームの仕事の様子を見ていると
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,まず仕事を始める前に\N祈りをささげています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,翻訳で難しくなったときでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:28.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバの聖霊に頼って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:30.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,良い判断や決定がなされるようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:34.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,祈って進めていたことは\N本当に印象的でした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:39.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,神の言葉がページから飛び出して\Nろう者の心に達するために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:42.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,幾つもの過程を踏む必要があります
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,ろう者が理解しやすい表現が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,慎重に検討されます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,マタイ 6:28の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,「野のユリ」を例に考えてみましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:59.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,今までマタイ 6章をはっきり\N理解できませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,「鳥」や「野のユリ」は\N「王国を……第一にする」ことと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:06.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,どんな関係があるんだろう？\Nと思っていました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:11.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,翻訳者は各自 内容を\N十分に理解できるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:13.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,原文を読み 調査します
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:17.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,次に チームミーティングで\Nアイデアを出し合って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:20.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖句の考えを手話に翻訳します
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,手話翻訳が完成したら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:27.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,割り当てを受けた兄弟が\Nプロンプト･ビデオを準備します
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,そのプロンプト･ビデオを見ながら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,スタジオ収録を行います
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:37.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,映像は丁寧に編集され
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,それから配信されます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:45.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,この例では 兄弟は花になりきり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,機織り機で花びらを織ったり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:52.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,それを自分の顔に\N縫い付けたりしています
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,それからこう問いかけます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,「こんなことはしませんよね？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,ページを飛び出した神の言葉は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,ろう者の心に届きます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが優しく教えて\Nくださっているのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,「王国を第一にするなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:13.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,必要なものは全て与えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,安心しなさい」ということ\Nだったんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,初めて分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,通勤途中の電車で見ていたのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,これがすごくいいビデオなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,夢中になって見ていたら\N降りるはずの駅を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,うっかり過ぎてしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,反対方向の電車に乗り換えたんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,ビデオを見ていてまたまた\N乗り過ごしてしまったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,それほど「マタイ」は楽しいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,神のかたちに造られている人間にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:53.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,本来持っている有益な感情\Nというものがあるわけですが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,残念ながらサタンの体制によって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,その有益な感情が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:04:00.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,奥へ奥へと押しやられています
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも神の言葉を人々に向けたり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:05.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちも神の言葉を読むと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:10.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,その本来持っている有益な\N感情が湧き上がってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:14.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,そういう力が神の言葉には\Nあるんだなっていうことを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,強く感じています
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,子供が父親に話しかけられて育つように
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:23.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが私の母語で話しかけて\Nくださるのを見ると
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,父としてエホバをもっと身近に感じます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,手話版の聖書が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:32.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,ろう者の心に語りかけている\Nっていうのがよく分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが本当に兄弟たちのことを\N愛しておられて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,ご自分の顔を輝かせておられる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,そういう様子を思い浮かべる\Nことができますし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:46.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟たちの顔も本当に光り\N輝いているように思います
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:50.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,心に響く言語で神の生きた言葉を見る時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,ろう者の兄弟姉妹は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:05:05.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが向けておられる笑顔を\N見ることができるのです
